                    <span>I enjoyed reading Dr. Blass's book on Stanley Milgram.
<br />Besides growing up in the same area in the Bronx as Milgram the book is a good read and does not drag. The Author really captured the character of his subject.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">An important book on an important man.</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
